This repository contains a react application that displays 3 blog posts. These can be clicked on to show the full blog post.
Additionally, 5 recent popular news stories from Google are shown in the right hand column. These are updated every 5 seconds with an ajax call
To run this react app, first make sure node npm are installed
After they are, download all the files from this repository
In the App.js component, the API KEY has to be added which will be given separately. Currently the value is just APIKEY it has to be replaced.
Navigate to this folder in terminal and then use the command npm start to start up the react up
